.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
House: ranch-style, art-deco, victorian, cottage
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, light-blue, brown, red
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, musician, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, pop, salsa, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, dutch, german
4 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, rat, turtle
 1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the american##1
 2. the dutch is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 4. the ranch-style house is on the left of the musician##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of soul is between the analyst and the person who likes red##2
 7. the german is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 9. the german is the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the firefighter is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
12. the art-deco house is the owner of the rat##1
13. the fan of salsa is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| House      | cottage        | victorian     | ranch-style        | art-deco    |
| Color          | brown     | light-blue   | blood-red   | red |
| Job           | security-guard | analyst  | firefighter | musician |
| Music-Genre   | pop            | salsa    | soul        | ambient  |
| Nationality   | dutch          | american | german      | british  |
| Pet           | mouse          | frog     | turtle      | rat      |

