.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, davidoff, swisher, cain
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, green, orange, fuchsia
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, chef, electrician, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, satire, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, german, indian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who likes green##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is the indian##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the analyst##1
 5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the french##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is between the electrician and the person who likes fuchsia##2
 8. the electrician is the german##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is between the owner of the mouse and the german##2
10. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who likes green##1
11. the manager is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
13. the person who likes orange is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar      | cain        | swisher      | davidoff | bolivar       |
| Color         | orange | blue | fuchsia   | green   |
| Job           | electrician | manager     | chef        | analyst   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | thriller    | documentary | satire    |
| Nationality   | german      | french      | indian      | brazilian |
| Pet           | ferret      | goldfish    | mouse       | hedgehog  |

