.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different games are played: domino, whist, snooker, go
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, puzzles, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, social-worker, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, satire, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, italian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, lizard, chinchilla
 1. the person playing domino is on the right of the social-worker##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is between the writer and the bartender##2
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing go##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fisherman##1
 5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the australian##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the owner of the horse and the british##2
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is between the australian and the owner of the goldfish##2
 8. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the writer##1
11. the fisherman is on the left of the british##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
13. the italian is the person playing domino##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |       3       |      4      |
| Game          | go     | snooker        | whist         | domino   |
| Hobby         | baking     | puzzles     | filmmaking    | woodworking |
| Job           | fisherman  | writer      | social-worker | bartender   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | time-travel | satire        | crime       |
| Nationality   | turkish    | british     | australian    | italian     |
| Pet     | goldfish | chinchilla       | lizard         | horse         |

