.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, tea, water
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit, lime, peach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, july, october
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, backgammon, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, family, western
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, russian, thai
 1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the mexican is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person eating lime is on the right of the pakistani##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the russian##1
10. the person eating peach is on the right of the person playing domino##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person drinking water and the person playing backgammon##2
13. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | water       | fanta         |
| Food          | cabbage | grapefruit  | lime        | peach         |
| Birthday         | july | april | january     | october   |
| Game           | backgammon | scrabble  | domino | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | western     | drama       | documentary   |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani   | thai        | mexican       |

