.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, eggplant, pepper, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, egyptian, french
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, designer, chef
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, orchid, dahlia
 1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the french is the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is the person eating pumpkin##1
 9. the dutch is the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the french is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the chef is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
12. the fisherman is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite     | mirinda  | iced-tea |
| Food          | artichoke     | pepper     | eggplant | pumpkin  |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | filmmaking | fishing  | sudoku   |
| Nationality   | dutch         | egyptian   | french   | canadian |
| Job         | fisherman       | designer    | chef   | coach |
| Flower     | dahlia        | zinnia   | orchid   | azalea      |

 